      <title>PVE因boot空间不足而升级失败的解决办法</title>
      <link>https://blog.margrop.net/post/pve-boot-space-not-enough-fail-upgrade/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Jan 2021 19:25:59 +0800</pubDate>
